description: Lists the engagements to a contact's contact channels.

parameters.name: ContactId
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the contact you are retrieving engagements for.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The pagination token to continue to the next page of results.

nested_items.name: Pages
nested_items.description: The list of engagements to a contact's contact channel.

nested_items.name: PageArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the page to the contact channel.

nested_items.name: EngagementArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the engagement that this page is part of.

nested_items.name: ContactArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the contact that Incident Manager is engaging.

nested_items.name: Sender
nested_items.description: The user that started the engagement.

nested_items.name: IncidentId
nested_items.description: The ARN of the incident that's engaging the contact channel.

nested_items.name: SentTime
nested_items.description: The time that Incident Manager engaged the contact channel.

nested_items.name: DeliveryTime
nested_items.description: The time the message was delivered to the contact channel.

nested_items.name: ReadTime
nested_items.description: The time that the contact channel acknowledged engagement.
